telemedpolska.pl.note: Telemedpolska.pl is the official representative of the European company TELEMED in Poland, offering reliable portable ultrasound devices to nearly 100 countries. They emphasize comprehensive and competent customer service, backed by over 30 years of experience, and tailor solutions to individual client needs.
